rows.label: qst660205_msg0001
rows.name:
Ooh, I've been waiting for someone
like you to show up!

rows.label: qst660205_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm an itinerant weaver of battle-songs!
My life's work is to take blood-curdling
tales and set them to sweet melodies...

rows.label: qst660205_msg0003
rows.name:
Would you mind telling me some
of yours? Not for free, of course.
One good turn deserves another.

rows.label: qst660205_msg0004
rows.name: Tell tales for Accessory Expander Kit?

rows.label: qst660205_msg0102
rows.name:
My, when I said "blood-curdling",
I didn't expect yours to curdle
quite so much of mine... Brr!

rows.label: qst660205_msg0103
rows.name:
But I am nothing if not inspired.
If you ever have more, please come 
and regale me again! I'll be waiting.

rows.label: qst660205_msg0201
rows.name:
You like to keep your cards
close to your chest, huh...

rows.label: qst660205_msg0202
rows.name:
Well, I'll be here if you change your
mind.

rows.label: qst660205_msg0301
rows.name:
I would surely enjoy hearing
more of your exploits. Alas...

rows.label: qst660205_msg0302
rows.name: I've run out of wares to trade you.
